01:34:17.950 --> 01:34:18.650
Qu'y a-t-il ?

01:34:19.320 --> 01:34:21.200
L'or a coulé !

01:34:21.530 --> 01:34:22.700
Quoi ?

01:34:23.330 --> 01:34:24.830
Non !

01:34:25.450 --> 01:34:27.040
Hi hi...

